 
ID: 1
Title: “Do koszyka” button is not visible for out of stock products.

Priority:
Medium

Severity:
Moderate

Environment:
https://zielarnia24.pl/najpopularniejsze-produkty,42.html
Windows 10 64 bit, 
Google Chrome version: 81.0.4044.114

Description:
After opening the link with the most popular product located on the down on the homepage, some of them are not available with the ‘Do koszyka” button.

Steps to reproduce:
    1.Go to website: zielarnia24.pl
    2.Scroll down to the “Najpopularniejsze produkty” tab and click.
    3.Find product ‘Korzeń rzewienia 50g Kawon’.

Expected result:
Available products are displayed on the page. Each of them has a button referring to the action (CTA). If the product is not available, ‘Powiadom o dostępności' button is displayed.

Actual result:
Available products are displayed on the page. If the product is not available, a rare button will not be displayed.

